{"tid":1229601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波：承認社會氣氛緊張　經濟民生難免受波及","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:49:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"e354a6b3ded61fa6c64a2108d23a881390c70f57","tid":1229601,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"政府宣布暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》，財政司司長陳茂波在網誌說，希望有助緩和過去一段時間，社會上繃緊的氣氛和張力，提供時間與空間，讓各方能回復在平靜中對話、理性商議。<br />\n<br />\n近日啟德商業地王被撻訂，陳茂波說，市場上對事件有不同解讀和猜測，莫衷一是，但他認為市場對土地需求仍然殷切，政府會盡快將有關用地重新招標。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，日前由於通往政府總部的公眾通道一度受阻，一幅正在招標的用地要延遲截標，當局會在未來一星期宣布新的截標日期。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波承認當社會氣氛緊張，一些經濟民生難免受到波及，但整體來說，香港的經濟及金融市場仍然穩健及有秩序地運作，當局會繼續監察市場情況及做好應對潛在風險的準備。"},{"pid":"3fa509db94bf48d900da543efaf6533f9aa4dc72","tid":1229601,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463145-20190616.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463145-20190616.htm&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=92d998f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463145-20190616.htm&h=86fc0a73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463145-20190616.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0a677edd8355a27e9b758856b21b10c588a03c65","tid":1229601,"uid":10733,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"還錢呀4000蚊呢撚樣"},{"pid":"4453b31e182fc8eb79084ddfc8fe8f7a33ae13a2","tid":1229601,"uid":37458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0a677edd8355a27e9b758856b21b10c588a03c65","tid":1229601,"uid":10733,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"還錢呀4000蚊呢撚樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma